{"word":"λειχήν","slug":"λειχήν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n62297\" key=\"leixh/n\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">λειχήν</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ῆνος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <sense id=\"n62297.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tree-moss, lichen</tr_>, implied in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> </bibl> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λειχηνιάω</foreign>). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n62297.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a kind of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">liver-wort</tr_>, that grows on damp rocks, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dsc.\">Dsc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.53</biblScope> </bibl>; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἵππειος λ.,</foreign> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἱππολειχήν</ref></xr>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0022.tlg001:945\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nic.\">Nic.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">945</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n62297.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">lichen-like eruption</tr_> on the skin of animals, esp. on the chin, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">mentagra</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg006.perseus-grc1:281\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a cl